videos.description: Joe Ingles drains a 3-pointer to break John Stockton's record for most made 3-pointers made in Utah Jazz franchise history.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Ingles breaks Stockton's Jazz 3-point record) 2021/01/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ingles breaks Stockton's Jazz 3-point record

videos.description: Mike Conley tosses up an alley-oop pass, and Rudy Gobert extends as he goes up to slam it down over Kristaps Porzingis.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Gobert extends for alley-oop slam over Porzingis) 2021/01/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gobert extends for alley-oop slam over Porzingis

videos.description: Josh Richardson flops to draw a foul call on Joe Ingles and create a Jazz turnover.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Richardson sells flop perfectly to ref) 2021/01/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Richardson sells flop perfectly to ref

videos.description: Dallas' Josh Green pulls off the slick reverse layup to the delight of the Mavericks' bench late in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Josh Green's crafty layup dazzles bench) 2021/1/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Josh Green's crafty layup dazzles bench
